Articles.Content: Hello all,been on vacation for a bit so wasn't able to post this on the forums when the video came out but I'm back in town now and wanted to share with you guys the video of my first manned mission to minmus. I was spurred on by my semi-successful probe to minmus and wanted to send up a Kerman to see how it would go. Hope you guys enjoy and as always I appreciate any advice of tips to help my future missions go more smoothly.
